<h2>Trip to Clark Quay<br /><span class="date">9th Oct 2022<span></h2>
<p>Wife and I took a much needed stroll down Clark Quay after eating a hearty dinner buffet at Ellenborough Market Cafe. Took some great photos of the amazing nightscape when combined with some great angles.</p>
