<h2>Wedding Anniversary @ Sentosa<br /><span class="date">4th Oct 2022<span></h2>
<p>I booked a room at Sofitel @ Sentosa for our wedding anniversary! It was warm and occasionally drizzly day but it produced incredible photoshots for us. We rode down the slopes on Skyline Luge, paced along the sea coast, watched the sunset before having a romantic Italian dinner at The Cliff.</p>
<a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/197341945@N07/52619418895/in/dateposted-public/" title="Sentosa Luge Skyride"><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/31337/52619418895_5e347f6bd2_z.jpg" width="640" height="360" alt="Sentosa Luge Skyride"></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>
